  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK967">
<l>oṭṭārpiṉ ceṉṟoruvaṉ vāḻtali ṉannilaiyē</l>
<l>keṭṭā ṉeṉappaṭuta ṉaṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is better for a man to be said of him that he died in his usual state than that he eked out his life by following those who disgraced him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
